        "q": "A bag has $5$ white and $5$ black balls. If two balls are drawn without replacement, what is the probability that the second ball is white given the first was black?",
        "q_zh": "一个袋子里有 $5$ 个白球和 $5$ 个黑球。如果不放回地取出两个球，已知第一个是黑球，第二个是白球的概率是多少？",
        "o": [
          "$\\frac{5}{10}$",
          "$\\frac{5}{9}$",
          "$\\frac{4}{9}$",
          "$\\frac{1}{2}$"
        ],
        "a": 1,
        "e": "After taking one black ball, there are still $5$ white balls left, but the total number of balls is now $9$. So $P = 5/9$.",
        "e_zh": "取走一个黑球后，还剩下 $5$ 个白球，但球的总数变成了 $9$。因此 $P = 5/9$。"
      },
